entries.partname: Alap, Jod and Gat in Jhaptal & Tintal
Alaap, slow Rupak, fast Tintal, Jhalla
Mori Gagar Na Bharam De, Drut
The new man of love and faith
Gat in Jhaptal, Drut Gat in Tintal
Ka Se Kahun Vilambit Ektal;Lagan Mori Laagi Drut Tintal
Vilambit ektas, drut tintal, addha tintal
Prabu Mohe Bharasaa Ek Tiharoo, Pariye Paarjanawa Ke Sajani
Shyam Bhaee, Ganashyam Nahi Aye More Dware
Gat - Bilambit Teental, Drut Ektal & Teental
